<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>예약목록</title>
<script>

</script>
<style>
table, td { 
border: 1px solid gray;
border-collapse: collapse;
padding: 10px;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<h1>예약목록</h1>
	<table>
		<tr>
			<td>예약번호</td>
			<td>숙소이름</td>
			<td>룸이름</td>
			<td>체크인/체크아웃</td>
